title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Cash 5' game
maintext:
OKLAHOMA CITY (AP) _ The winning numbers in Tuesday evening’s drawing of the Oklahoma Lottery’s “Cash 5” game were:
10-19-26-29-36
(ten, nineteen, twenty-six, twenty-nine, thirty-six)
